FIG. 2. 
<taxonomicName authority="Nogueira, 2001" authorityName="Nogueira" authorityYear="2001" box="[185,438,1508,1530]" class="Polychaeta" family="Syllidae" genus="Sphaerosyllis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="9" pageNumber="1780" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="brasiliensis" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[185,438,1508,1530]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="1780">Sphaerosyllis brasiliensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[458,520,1508,1529]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1780" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
: (A) anterior part, dorsal view (holotype); (B) posterior part, dorsal view (holotype); (C) compound chaetae, anterior parapodium; (D) acicula, anterior parapodium; (E) dorsal simple chaeta; (F) compound chaetae, posterior parapodium; (G) ventral simple chaeta; (H) aciculum, posterior parapodium. Scale bar: (A, B) 0.55 mm; (C±H) 20 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[694,707,1614,1636]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="1780">m</emphasis>
m.
